reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Makes packing so much easier and more organized
reviews.reviewText: I got a new suitcase and it comes with zippered sections to keep items from moving as much during travel and I was shocked at how much of a difference it made. However I have 5 kids and I'm not wanting to buy everyone new suitcases right now. These are the perfection solution. They are lightweight but durable and it is very easy to pack each individual one and pop them into the suitcase, or put them in the empty suitcase, fill them up, then zip them closed. They make the suitcase have compartments if they aren't already built in, and keep items separated and organized. I also love it for keeping dirty clothes separate at the end of the trip.They also all fit into each other when empty so they don't take up much room at all

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Packing bags breathable, store quite easily, fast shipping!
reviews.reviewText: Got these tonight! I have tons of bags for all sort of things and I would say the material quality is pretty good, but it is also the really lightweight material we find in the drawstring backpacks. The stiching and the closures are all higher quality done so they should last longer. The see thru areas are a mesh material. Of course this allows for your clothes or items to breathe and stay fresh or closer to it. They all roll up into the small travel bag. Super easy to keep together and store!Cons: they are not as deep as the picture shows more like 2 to 2.5 inches deep. However, packing small and medium suitcases these would be perfect. I took pictures of what all came in the 8 piece set. If there was 1 or two larger bags I would say it would easily be great for a larger suitcase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great way to stay Organized
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased these eight-piece packing cubes to use on our cruise and have our clothes seperated in one suitcase. They have been an absolute game-changer for my travels! These cubes are a must-have for anyone looking to stay organized and make packing a breeze.One of the standout features is the perfect fit these cubes provide in my suitcase. They slide in effortlessly, utilizing every inch of space efficiently. Once we were in our stateroom, all I had to do is take out the organizers, and voilà - I have quick and easy access to all my clothes. No more rummaging through my luggage!The lightweight design of these cubes is another huge plus. They add virtually no extra weight to my suitcase, allowing me to maximize my packing capacity without worrying about exceeding weight limits.These packing cubes have truly simplified my travel experience. They keep my clothes neatly separated, and the mesh tops allow me to identify items quickly. It's like having a mini dresser in your suitcase!Whether you're a frequent traveler or just someone who likes to stay organized on trips, these packing cubes are a game-changer. They've made packing and unpacking a breeze, and I can't imagine traveling without them now. Highly recommended!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this bags to make it easier to pack my twins clothes separately and stuff they needed in our big suitcase. First bag I unzipped the zipper literally came unstitched from the bag. Second bag I tried did the same thing. The stitches just come apart. The bag is super thin and can’t hold. I ended up packing their tiny clothes socks etc in the suit case and when I opened it everything was everywhere. Hate it them! Won’t be buying again.
